19
00:10:40.100 --> 00:10:52.140
Pedro: 4237 has always tried to achieve account abstraction in a way that was completely off-chain, in a way made it optional for you to actually have account abstraction, and even with 7702,

20
00:10:52.140 --> 00:11:00.300
Pedro: Like, being present on-chain with this new transaction type, it still means that you are not, by default.

21
00:11:00.590 --> 00:11:09.769
